 K,) from Lh, (TA,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^ayoramiY~N", "text_ar": "اَيْرَمِىٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (T, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A sign,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mark, set up to show the way;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "stones set up as a sign,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "mark, to show the way in the desert:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) or particularly"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "one belonging to"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the tribe of"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]'"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Ád:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) accord. to ISh, the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iram", "text_ar": "اـِرَم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a thing"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "like a man in a standing posture upon the head of a hill, whereby one is directed to the right way, and whereby the land is marked, composed of stones set one upon another, and is only the work of the Muslims, and such is made by people in the present day, upon the road:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such as was made by the people in the time of ignorance, who were accustomed, when they found a thing in their way and could not take it with them, to leave upon it some stones, whereby to know it, until, when they returned, they took it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) the pl. [of pauc.] is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A=raAmN", "text_ar": "ا=رَامٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and [of mult.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uruwmN", "text_ar": "اُرُومٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(ISh, T, S, M, K:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^uruwmN", "text_ar": "اُرُومٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "graves,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sepulchres, of"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the tribe of"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]'"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Ád."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K.)       -A2-  ["}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iramN", "text_ar": "اـِرَمٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iramu *aAtu AlEimaAdi", "text_ar": "اـِرَمُ ذَاتُ العِمَادِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(see art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Emd", "text_ar": "عمد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") is a proper name; but whether of a place, or a tribe, or an individual, is disputed: it is commonly believed to be the name of"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The terrestrial paradise of Sheddád the son of 'Ád:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "see Bd lxxxix. 6.]"}], "source_refs": ["T", "S", "M", "K", "TA", "ISh"]}, {"entry_id": "n16560", "headword_ar": "ارمّ", "root": "rm", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", said of a bone,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It had in it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contained,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rim~", "text_ar": "رِمّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "marrow,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, S, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "running therein."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) One says of a sheep or goat (S, M) that is lean, or emaciated, (S,) and of a she-camel, (M,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA yurim~u minohaA maDoribN", "text_ar": "مَا يُرِمُّ مِنْهَا مَضْرِبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, M,) meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Not a bone of her that is broken and from which the marrow is"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sought to be"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "extracted"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contains any marrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (M:) i. e., if any of her bones be broken, no marrow will be found in it. (S.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Arm~t", "text_ar": "ارمّت"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is said of a she-camel in the first stage of fatness when becoming in good condition of body, and in the last stage thereof when becoming lean; (M, TA;) meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "She had in her somewhat of marrow."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) ―         -b2-  See also 1, in the latter part of the paragraph, in four places.       -A2-  Also, (T, S, M, K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_iromaAmN", "text_ar": "اـِرْمَامٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (T,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a man, T)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, silent;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, M, K;) in a general sense; or, as some say,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from fear,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "fright:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M:) [and in like manner a bird: see its part. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "murim~N", "text_ar": "مُرِمٌّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":] or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "they"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a company of men)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "were,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, silent."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) [See also R. Q. 2.]       -A3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Arm~", "text_ar": "ارمّ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ilaY All~ahow", "text_ar": "اـِلَى اللَّهْو"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He inclined to diversion, sport,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "play."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IAar, M, K.) ―         -b2-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Arm~ lika*aA", "text_ar": "ارمّ لِكَذَا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He was cheered,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "delighted,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pleased,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was diverted, by reason of such a thing;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aran~a lahu", "text_ar": "اَرَنَّ لَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (T in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rn", "text_ar": "رن"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".)"}], "source_refs": ["T", "S", "K", "M"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}